nowboarder will keep his spinning momentum due to the low friction on the rails or curbs material, the same is true for air-time, what allows you to do spins on rails, curbs or in air-time.\n\nGameplay\n\u2022 Level System (only one level at the moment)\n\u2022 Score System\n\u2022 To-Do-List for each map\n\u2022 Map - \"Mount Pee Pee\"\n\n\u2022 [up coming] Map - \"Ski-Hall\"\n\u2022 [up coming] Map - \"Woods\"\n\u2022 [up coming] Freestyle-Mode\n\u2022 [up coming] Recording & Filming\n\u2022 [up coming] Freestyle-Mode\n\u2022 [up coming] Board Editor", "short_description": "Snowboard Funpark is a virtual reality snowboard experience. Do slides, grinds, spins and more in \"Snowboard Funpark\"."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/snowboardfunpark-privacypolicy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "YueWorks", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://yue-beifong.jimdosite.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "430646418950439"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "802609904515723"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "802609904515723"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1655676000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "802609904515723"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "5399840543437232", "ver